-- Deutsche Boerse Aims to Grow on Its Own, Francioni Tells FTD
-- B y   O l i v e r   S u e s s
-- 2012-02-05T17:48:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-05/deutsche-boerse-aims-to-grow-on-its-own-francioni-tells-ftd.html
Deutsche Boerse AG (DB1)  aims to grow on
its own following the failed combination with  NYSE Euronext (NYX) ,
Chief Executive Officer  Reto Francioni  told  Financial Times
Deutschland  in an interview.  Frankfurt-based Deutsche Boerse will focus its expansion on
areas such as derivatives clearing, risk management and
collateral management as well as international growth, FTD cited
Francioni as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Oliver Suess in Munich at 
